snippet.title: GROUND-UNBOUND | Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1760020/GROUNDUNBOUND/
WISHLIST NOW!

GROUND-UNBOUND is a procedurally generated, high-intensity movement shooter with a retro wave art style. It features roguelike mechanics with a number of skills, guns and abilities to play with, including a variety of enemy types to shoot at. Created during the 7-Day BigFry Game Jam, updated for steam release.

Shoutout To Frosty For Helping Overhaul The Art!

Trailer Music: Jacklikeschez
